Subject: [PATCH v15 089/115] KVM: TDX: Add a place holder for handler of TDX hypercalls (TDG.VP.VMCALL)
Date:   Tue, 25 Jul 2023 15:14:40 -0700
Message-Id: <4b6737290264b1938f16f9de4ce7613a98de7454.1690322424.git.isaku.yamahata@intel.com>
X-Mailer: git-send-email 2.25.1
